sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    Note right of browser: User types a note into the text field
    Note right of browser: User clicks "Save"

    Note right of browser: SPA JavaScript prevents default form submit
    Note right of browser: SPA creates a new note object (content + date)

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa\nContent-Type: application/json\nBody: { "content": "<user text>", "date": "<timestamp>" }
    activate server
    Note right of server: Server stores the new note
    server-->>browser: 201 Created (or 200 OK)\nResponse: {"message":"note created"}
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: SPA updates UI locally (re-renders notes list)\nwithout reloading the page
